Package ca.openosp.openo.rx.erx.model.request

Class GetPrescriptions5

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.rx.erx.model.request.GetPrescriptions5
public class GetPrescriptions5 extends Object
Provides an interface for the the External Prescriber GetPrescriptions5 method, which must be called by sending a SOAP request to the External Prescriber's www service.
